_header: O good Harry the Sixth by name
Subjects: Henry VI, song in praise of
_description: James Ryman, Song in praise of Henry VI — eight stanzas rhyme royal

CULEe112.First Lines:
O good Herry the sixte by nameBothe of Inglond ye & of
                    ffraunce…
CULEe112.Last Lines:
…That he will graunte vs of his graceIn blisse with the to
                    haue a place
